Package: PeakRankR
Title: Rank Genomic Peaks by Coverage and Magnitude Across Cell Types
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Saroja",
           family = "Somasundaram",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sarojas@alleninstitute.org")
Description: 
    PeakRankR provides a pipeline to summarize BigWig signal over genomic regions, 
    compute cell-type-specific ranks using coverage proportion and signal magnitude, 
    and extract the top-ranked peaks per sample. 
    Optionally supports weighting rank components and generating UCSC Genome Browser links.
